Package compiler

Enum Statement

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Statement>
compiler.Statement
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Statement>, java.lang.constant.Constable
enum Statement extends Enum<Statement>
A collection of the different statements that are supported by the high-level language. Each statement checks a line of high-level code for its syntax and also evaluates it assuming both that it is syntactically correct and that all variables and constants are correctly declared.
Author:
Alex Mandelias
